_sText:
aim_fightyard_dev
by Starving Hobo


This map is a small dev arena with several stories.

The waterfalls function as ladders which you climb to reach the higher levels and at the top level there is an outer ring which can be accessed via two bridges.  On the inside there are two waterfalls which will take you straight to the top.

Thanks to TopHATTWaffle for the waterfall texture!
